WEBVTT

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.208
girls who were born to race.

00:00:07.958 --> 00:00:09.333
Some had a rocky fate.

00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:13.917
Some left behind a legacy.
In this wondrous world,

00:00:13.917 --> 00:00:16.542
they continued their journey via racing.

00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:19.958
That is their destiny.

00:00:20.542 --> 00:00:24.458
The race toward the best

00:00:24.458 --> 00:00:26.458
is still unfinished.

00:00:27.375 --> 00:00:29.500
So they run

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:31.833
and run

00:00:31.833 --> 00:00:33.917
toward the finishing line.

00:00:36.875 --> 00:00:40.458
The horse girls
are heading into the third bend.

00:00:40.458 --> 00:00:44.750
Who will win the triple crown
of Satsuki Sho?

00:00:44.750 --> 00:00:46.708
Me. It's going to be me.

00:00:46.708 --> 00:00:48.833
I have never lost once.

00:00:48.833 --> 00:00:51.417
I will win Satsuki Sho
like Tokai Teio did.

00:00:52.333 --> 00:00:55.000
The popular Satono Crown
is following closely behind.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:58.125
Will we witness the birth
of the long-awaited Satsuki Sho champion?

00:00:58.125 --> 00:01:01.833
Will Satono Crown
accomplish her family's wish?

00:01:02.833 --> 00:01:03.958
Duramente!

00:01:03.958 --> 00:01:06.417
She changed outward.

00:01:06.417 --> 00:01:09.625
This is the final stretch.
Other athletes are closing in.

00:01:09.625 --> 00:01:11.292
But the inside line
is occupied by the leading athletes.

00:01:11.292 --> 00:01:12.750
Satono Crown is in the middle of the pack.

00:01:12.750 --> 00:01:14.042
Can she close the gap?

00:01:14.042 --> 00:01:15.917
The final stretch isn't a long one.

00:01:15.917 --> 00:01:19.167
In the final stretch,
Gentsu Steel appeared!

00:01:19.167 --> 00:01:20.417
200 meters left.

00:01:20.417 --> 00:01:22.375
Kitasan Black is accelerating.

00:01:22.375 --> 00:01:23.583
Kitasan Black!

00:01:23.583 --> 00:01:26.458
-I have to win this.
-Kitasan Black is in the inside line.

00:01:26.458 --> 00:01:28.917
Can she overtake Kitasan Black? She did!

00:01:28.917 --> 00:01:31.417
Gentsu Steel is taking a small lead.

00:01:31.417 --> 00:01:33.917
Duramente appears on the side.

00:01:33.917 --> 00:01:36.458
Duramente! Can you believe it?

00:01:36.458 --> 00:01:38.833
She's so fast.

00:01:38.833 --> 00:01:41.583
Has she always been this strong?

00:01:41.583 --> 00:01:43.583
Duramente!

00:01:44.333 --> 00:01:45.625
Astounding!

00:01:45.625 --> 00:01:48.958
Duramente won Satsuki Sho.

00:01:48.958 --> 00:01:49.542
Is this

00:01:49.542 --> 00:01:50.625
-Yes!
-what you call

00:01:50.625 --> 00:01:51.875
a god-given talent?

00:01:51.875 --> 00:01:54.000
I can't believe it!

00:01:56.000 --> 00:02:02.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

00:02:08.917 --> 00:02:12.625
I…

00:02:12.625 --> 00:02:15.042
I lost.

00:02:22.375 --> 00:02:25.417
EPISODE 1: THE LINE IN SIGHT

00:02:26.917 --> 00:02:29.375
TOKAI TEIO
CAN TEIO SURPASS THE EMPEROR?

00:02:36.667 --> 00:02:38.625
KITASAN BLACK

00:02:38.625 --> 00:02:40.708
Morning, Kita.

00:02:40.708 --> 00:02:42.208
Morning, Diamond.

00:02:42.208 --> 00:02:44.542
You're up early today. Be safe.

00:02:44.542 --> 00:02:45.500
I will.

00:02:45.500 --> 00:02:46.583
See you then.

00:02:46.583 --> 00:02:48.083
See you.

00:02:48.583 --> 00:02:50.708
SATONO DIAMOND

00:02:56.417 --> 00:02:57.708
Satsuki Sho,

00:02:57.708 --> 00:02:59.083
my first G1

00:02:59.083 --> 00:03:00.667
and my first defeat.

00:03:00.667 --> 00:03:02.042
Everyone is very strong there.

00:03:02.042 --> 00:03:04.667
And the pressure is through the roof.

00:03:04.667 --> 00:03:07.083
The next race will be the Japanese Derby.

00:03:07.083 --> 00:03:08.958
The race everyone looks forward to.

00:03:10.333 --> 00:03:14.083
I will race like the ever-awesome Teio.

00:03:14.708 --> 00:03:16.333
Teio…

00:03:16.333 --> 00:03:17.375
All right.

00:03:17.375 --> 00:03:19.708
Here I come!

00:03:19.708 --> 00:03:20.833
Eh?

00:03:25.458 --> 00:03:27.667
Are you all right, ma'am?

00:03:28.250 --> 00:03:30.083
My back hurts a bit

00:03:30.083 --> 00:03:32.417
so I sat down to rest.

00:03:32.417 --> 00:03:34.500
Where do you live? I can carry you back.

00:03:34.500 --> 00:03:37.208
It's okay. I live nearby.

00:03:38.292 --> 00:03:40.458
Grab tight.

00:03:41.167 --> 00:03:43.292
Let's go!

00:03:43.708 --> 00:03:46.208
Let's go!

00:03:46.875 --> 00:03:48.708
Thank you.

00:03:48.708 --> 00:03:49.792
You're welcome.

00:03:49.792 --> 00:03:50.875
Goodbye.

00:03:51.833 --> 00:03:52.792
All right.

00:03:52.792 --> 00:03:55.167
Let's do this.

00:03:56.375 --> 00:03:57.500
Eh?

00:03:58.333 --> 00:04:00.000
How are you?

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.833
Do you know where Tokyo Racecourse is?

00:04:01.833 --> 00:04:05.125
Pardon. I can't speak English.

00:04:05.125 --> 00:04:06.708
"TOKYO RACECOURSE"
This one.

00:04:06.708 --> 00:04:07.792
"TOKYO RACECOURSE"
Okay. Okay.

00:04:08.208 --> 00:04:11.000
Okay…

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.167
"CURRENT LOCATION"
This!

00:04:12.167 --> 00:04:13.583
"HERE"
This is very detailed.

00:04:13.583 --> 00:04:15.375
Good luck!

00:04:15.792 --> 00:04:16.833
Done.

00:04:16.833 --> 00:04:19.292
I should head back to Tracen Academy now.

00:04:19.958 --> 00:04:23.708
A punctured tire!

00:04:26.917 --> 00:04:28.750
You can run so fast.

00:04:29.667 --> 00:04:32.000
Thank you, Kita.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.417
Don't mention it.

00:04:33.417 --> 00:04:34.958
It helps with my training too.

00:04:34.958 --> 00:04:36.000
Thank you so much.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:37.292
You're welcome.

00:04:37.292 --> 00:04:39.583
Dad taught me to help others,

00:04:39.583 --> 00:04:42.292
to cheer others,

00:04:42.292 --> 00:04:45.458
and to put a smile on everyone's face.

00:04:45.458 --> 00:04:47.500
You're so kind, Kita.

00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:49.000
Ever so helpful.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.500
You are a great help.

00:04:50.500 --> 00:04:54.583
I know, right? Your presence
always cheers everyone up.

00:04:55.167 --> 00:04:57.625
Thank you, great helper!

00:04:57.625 --> 00:04:59.208
By the way, what is the time now?

00:05:01.042 --> 00:05:02.000
Morning.

00:05:04.042 --> 00:05:05.917
What's taking Kita so long?

00:05:05.917 --> 00:05:07.125
Sheesh.

00:05:07.125 --> 00:05:08.958
Diamond!

00:05:12.875 --> 00:05:14.458
I'm so sorry.

00:05:14.458 --> 00:05:16.375
You shouldn't push yourself too far.

00:05:16.375 --> 00:05:18.042
You just completed a race.

00:05:18.583 --> 00:05:19.750
Right.

00:05:20.667 --> 00:05:21.833
Come, Kita.

00:05:21.833 --> 00:05:22.917
Okay.

00:05:23.333 --> 00:05:24.875
What is the first period?

00:05:24.875 --> 00:05:26.542
Home economics.

00:05:26.542 --> 00:05:28.667
Urgh, that scary teacher again.

00:05:29.917 --> 00:05:30.750
This first…

00:05:30.750 --> 00:05:31.458
"HOMEMAKING ROOM"
This first…

00:05:31.458 --> 00:05:32.750
"HOMEMAKING ROOM"
Then this…

00:05:32.875 --> 00:05:35.167
Then this…

00:05:35.167 --> 00:05:36.250
Ow!

00:05:36.250 --> 00:05:37.792
Are you all right?

00:05:37.792 --> 00:05:39.333
Show me your finger, Kita.

00:05:39.333 --> 00:05:40.875
Thanks a lot, Diamond.

00:05:40.875 --> 00:05:43.583
You have to be careful with needles.

00:05:44.500 --> 00:05:46.917
"DERBY"
I couldn't stop thinking about the race.

00:05:46.917 --> 00:05:48.875
"DERBY"
It's around the corner.

00:05:49.292 --> 00:05:53.167
If only I could debut together with you.

00:05:53.833 --> 00:05:54.958
Diamond…

00:05:56.625 --> 00:05:59.500
Have you always been good at embroidering?

00:05:59.500 --> 00:06:00.417
Not at all.

00:06:00.417 --> 00:06:02.917
I merely follow
the teacher's instructions.

00:06:02.917 --> 00:06:05.000
As expected from you then.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:07.375
You're a fast learner.

00:06:07.375 --> 00:06:10.458
I am so clumsy compared to you.

00:06:10.458 --> 00:06:12.458
DERBY

00:06:12.917 --> 00:06:13.833
"JAPANESE DERBY"
Answer this question.

00:06:14.333 --> 00:06:19.708
190,000 audiences cheered
as Ines Fujin won the Derby.

00:06:19.708 --> 00:06:21.417
The next one who won…

00:06:21.417 --> 00:06:23.000
-I know the answer.
-Yes, Kitasan Black?

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.250
It's Tokai Teio.

00:06:24.250 --> 00:06:25.958
Exactly.

00:06:25.958 --> 00:06:28.708
The one who won the Derby
before Mihono Bourbon…

00:06:28.708 --> 00:06:30.292
It's Tokai Teio.

00:06:30.292 --> 00:06:31.708
Yes.

00:06:32.125 --> 00:06:35.042
Kita, you're on fire today.

00:06:35.042 --> 00:06:37.625
Let's train together.

00:06:37.625 --> 00:06:39.833
You're even more excited after school.

00:06:39.833 --> 00:06:42.708
Because I get to see Teio in person.

00:06:42.708 --> 00:06:46.000
If only you were on my team.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:49.000
Sorry that I went to another team…

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:52.125
For the Satono family,
that team holds a special meaning.

00:06:52.917 --> 00:06:56.000
The trainers and other athletes
of Team Capella

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:58.458
are all fighting for their dreams.

00:06:58.458 --> 00:07:00.208
We all share a common goal.

00:07:00.958 --> 00:07:02.917
Here you are, Kita.

00:07:03.958 --> 00:07:06.125
Yes, yes.

00:07:06.125 --> 00:07:07.167
It is I, the come-and-go,

00:07:07.167 --> 00:07:08.542
"SAKURA BAKUSHIN O"
Sakura Bakushin O.

00:07:09.333 --> 00:07:11.708
See you later, Kita.

00:07:12.167 --> 00:07:13.792
Diamond, wait for me!

00:07:13.792 --> 00:07:15.292
After your debut,

00:07:15.292 --> 00:07:18.042
I can tell that there's something special
to your gait.

00:07:18.042 --> 00:07:21.000
That's right. I can feel the dormant,

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.917
explosive power inside you.

00:07:22.917 --> 00:07:26.083
I think you're perfect for a sprint.

00:07:26.083 --> 00:07:29.875
So let's rise to the top of sprinting.

00:07:29.875 --> 00:07:31.583
Come.

00:07:31.583 --> 00:07:32.792
Uhm…

00:07:32.792 --> 00:07:35.167
I'm in Spica now.

00:07:35.167 --> 00:07:36.208
Sorry.

00:07:36.208 --> 00:07:38.250
Why?

00:07:43.375 --> 00:07:44.708
Sigh.

00:07:44.708 --> 00:07:47.750
I know she means well.

00:07:47.750 --> 00:07:50.375
She is quite nice, but…

00:07:52.667 --> 00:07:55.375
As usual, you're the first, Kita.

00:07:55.375 --> 00:07:55.583
Special! Suzuka!

00:07:55.583 --> 00:07:56.792
"SPECIAL WEEK, SILENCE SUZUKA"
Special! Suzuka!

00:07:56.792 --> 00:07:57.958
"SPECIAL WEEK, SILENCE SUZUKA"
Hello.

00:07:58.083 --> 00:08:00.458
Thank you for cleaning up the place, Kita.

00:08:00.458 --> 00:08:01.708
Don't mention it.

00:08:01.708 --> 00:08:03.708
Here. Thanks for tidying up.

00:08:04.375 --> 00:08:05.708
"DAIWA SCARLET, VODKA"
Thanks.

00:08:05.708 --> 00:08:06.917
"DAIWA SCARLET, VODKA"
It was a gift, anyway.

00:08:06.917 --> 00:08:08.167
Don't worry about it.

00:08:08.167 --> 00:08:09.875
You bought it just now.

00:08:09.875 --> 00:08:10.958
We agreed not to tell her!

00:08:10.958 --> 00:08:11.500
Move aside.

00:08:11.500 --> 00:08:12.792
"GOLD SHIP"
Move aside.

00:08:12.792 --> 00:08:16.042
"GOLD SHIP"
I'm ready to fight Takarazuka Kinen…

00:08:16.042 --> 00:08:18.042
All right. I'm done.

00:08:18.042 --> 00:08:19.542
TEIO'S RACE

00:08:20.875 --> 00:08:21.792
JAPANESE DERBY, TOKYO RACECOURSE
2,400M LAP

00:08:22.333 --> 00:08:23.458
You're watching it again.

00:08:23.458 --> 00:08:25.042
Don't you get sick of it,
watching it every day?

00:08:25.042 --> 00:08:26.542
It's good to do some research.

00:08:26.542 --> 00:08:29.917
I highly doubt she's researching.

00:08:30.667 --> 00:08:33.000
She looks so awesome.

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:35.207
She breezed through her rivals,

00:08:35.207 --> 00:08:37.749
blitzed through her enemies.

00:08:37.750 --> 00:08:41.000
Please do this when I'm not here.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.332
Teio!

00:08:42.332 --> 00:08:42.666
You never change at all.

00:08:42.667 --> 00:08:44.792
"TOKAI TEIO, MEJIRO MCQUEEN"
You never change at all.

00:08:44.792 --> 00:08:45.792
"TOKAI TEIO, MEJIRO MCQUEEN"
Are you blushing?

00:08:46.083 --> 00:08:47.125
Not at all.

00:08:47.125 --> 00:08:49.292
Uhm, Teio.

00:08:49.292 --> 00:08:51.083
When you competed in the Derby,

00:08:51.083 --> 00:08:54.500
what went on in your mind before the race?

00:08:55.167 --> 00:08:56.625
Hmm.

00:08:58.125 --> 00:09:00.875
I thought about the winner's interview.

00:09:00.875 --> 00:09:03.750
She was already thinking about
the things to do after the victory.

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:05.292
I—I see…

00:09:05.292 --> 00:09:06.333
Woah.

00:09:06.333 --> 00:09:09.333
Also, I thought about proving
my worth to Rudolf.

00:09:09.333 --> 00:09:10.333
What about you, Special?

00:09:10.333 --> 00:09:14.042
I could only think about charging in.

00:09:14.042 --> 00:09:16.375
You're all here.

00:09:16.375 --> 00:09:18.542
Get changed and gather by the track.

00:09:18.542 --> 00:09:19.833
Don't be late.

00:09:20.542 --> 00:09:21.958
Listen up, Kita.

00:09:21.958 --> 00:09:24.875
The track in this Derby is 400 meters
longer than the track in Satsuki Sho.

00:09:24.875 --> 00:09:27.167
The straights in Fuchu are long,

00:09:27.167 --> 00:09:30.208
which are not great
for runners of your type.

00:09:30.208 --> 00:09:36.125
You'll meet runners who save up a burst
like Crown or Duramente.

00:09:36.583 --> 00:09:39.750
However, it's too risky
to change your gait now,

00:09:39.750 --> 00:09:42.542
so you will play it to your advantage.

00:09:42.542 --> 00:09:44.917
You'll focus on your stamina,
and then, your endurance.

00:09:44.917 --> 00:09:47.208
Run at your own pace.

00:09:47.208 --> 00:09:48.500
Do not be distracted by your rivals.

00:09:48.500 --> 00:09:50.792
"DURAMENTE"
Do not be distracted by your rivals.

00:09:51.042 --> 00:09:53.292
Let's give it a try first.

00:09:53.292 --> 00:09:54.708
Yes!

00:09:54.708 --> 00:10:00.125
Go!

00:10:00.125 --> 00:10:02.083
Kita is very motivated.

00:10:02.083 --> 00:10:02.917
Indeed.

00:10:02.917 --> 00:10:09.333
Charge!

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:11.708
Kitasan Black.

00:10:11.708 --> 00:10:11.917
Crown.

00:10:11.917 --> 00:10:12.875
"SATONO CROWN"
Crown.

00:10:12.875 --> 00:10:14.167
"SATONO CROWN"
Do you think you can win the Derby?

00:10:14.167 --> 00:10:15.000
Do you think you can win the Derby?

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:16.625
I will.

00:10:16.625 --> 00:10:18.500
I have to.

00:10:18.500 --> 00:10:22.000
The angle I took in Satsuki Sho
put me at a disadvantage.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:24.958
I have to improve myself
before I win the race.

00:10:24.958 --> 00:10:26.125
Yeah.

00:10:26.125 --> 00:10:28.958
I will win the first G1

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:30.458
for our family.

00:10:49.417 --> 00:10:51.000
If this carries on…

00:10:56.958 --> 00:11:00.958
UMA MUSUME PRETTY DERBY SEASON 3

00:11:00.958 --> 00:11:02.917
DERBY

00:11:54.458 --> 00:11:55.625
Derby…

00:11:55.625 --> 00:11:58.125
A once-in-a-lifetime stage.

00:11:58.125 --> 00:12:00.292
The same tournament Teio took part in.

00:12:00.750 --> 00:12:02.708
I have to…

00:12:22.292 --> 00:12:25.625
Tomorrow is the day.
Who do you think will win?

00:12:25.625 --> 00:12:27.167
Duramente, I think.

00:12:27.167 --> 00:12:28.875
She is very strong.

00:12:28.875 --> 00:12:31.542
Some might even say she's a prodigy.

00:12:31.542 --> 00:12:33.083
You may cross now.

00:12:34.583 --> 00:12:36.458
Satono Crown might win too.

00:12:36.458 --> 00:12:38.500
She is promising.

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:39.625
What about Kitasan Black?

00:12:39.625 --> 00:12:41.500
She was very close last time.

00:12:41.500 --> 00:12:43.333
But the track there is too long for her.

00:12:52.208 --> 00:12:53.417
Kita.

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.958
Diamond, are you going back now?

00:12:55.958 --> 00:12:59.083
Yes. You train very hard every day.

00:12:59.083 --> 00:13:01.083
Because Derby is around the corner.

00:13:02.125 --> 00:13:04.708
I'll get changed now. Give me a minute.

00:13:04.708 --> 00:13:05.625
Okay.

00:13:07.292 --> 00:13:08.667
As you can see here,

00:13:08.667 --> 00:13:11.333
the streets of Fuchu
are teeming with people

00:13:11.333 --> 00:13:14.417
on the eve of the Japanese Derby.

00:13:14.417 --> 00:13:16.417
Everyone is excited.

00:13:16.417 --> 00:13:19.000
-I can't wait.
-Yeah.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.292
I can't wait.

00:13:20.292 --> 00:13:21.500
I can't wait.

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:22.500
I can't wait.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:24.000
I can't wait.

00:13:25.292 --> 00:13:26.583
Yummy.

00:13:26.583 --> 00:13:28.250
Diamond.

00:13:28.250 --> 00:13:30.250
How is Crown doing?

00:13:30.875 --> 00:13:32.417
She's quite relaxed

00:13:32.417 --> 00:13:34.375
and she told me
that she was in great form.

00:13:34.375 --> 00:13:35.542
I see.

00:13:37.833 --> 00:13:42.500
It's unusual of you to ask about others.

00:13:42.500 --> 00:13:44.250
Oh.

00:13:45.333 --> 00:13:49.375
If you were racing in the Derby tomorrow,

00:13:50.333 --> 00:13:53.708
what do you think you'd think about
when you're running?

00:13:53.708 --> 00:13:54.958
Winning the race.

00:13:54.958 --> 00:13:56.375
That's all.

00:13:57.417 --> 00:13:59.667
My family's curse will not be broken

00:13:59.667 --> 00:14:02.000
unless I have a firm resolution.

00:14:02.792 --> 00:14:05.875
No one can predict the outcome,

00:14:06.375 --> 00:14:07.583
but…

00:14:07.583 --> 00:14:12.375
But you will definitely lose
if you don't have faith in yourself.

00:14:12.375 --> 00:14:14.125
Don't you agree, Kita?

00:14:15.208 --> 00:14:16.500
I…

00:14:24.583 --> 00:14:29.000
G1 is still new to me.

00:14:29.667 --> 00:14:31.542
I'm seeing so many new things.

00:14:32.167 --> 00:14:33.500
And the Derby is…

00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:35.833
It's going to be more overwhelming.

00:14:36.875 --> 00:14:39.625
I can't be as confident as everyone.

00:14:40.917 --> 00:14:42.000
I see.

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:44.875
So you are afraid of the race.

00:14:46.125 --> 00:14:47.708
I think so, yeah.

00:14:47.708 --> 00:14:50.625
No matter how hard I train,
I feel like I don't stand a chance.

00:14:51.708 --> 00:14:52.917
I'm scared.

00:14:56.583 --> 00:14:59.583
Let me interview the public.

00:14:59.583 --> 00:15:02.083
The Japanese Derby is tomorrow.

00:15:02.083 --> 00:15:05.042
Yes, my kid is looking forward to it.

00:15:05.042 --> 00:15:06.167
Yes!

00:15:06.167 --> 00:15:08.583
It's like a festival!

00:15:09.375 --> 00:15:11.667
It's like a festival.

00:15:13.500 --> 00:15:15.750
She's such a cute girl, Kita.

00:15:16.958 --> 00:15:18.208
Kita?

00:15:18.208 --> 00:15:19.625
Festival…

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:23.292
A festival.

00:15:24.208 --> 00:15:26.208
-It is a festival.
-Yes.

00:15:26.208 --> 00:15:28.625
It is a festival.

00:15:29.667 --> 00:15:30.917
I…

00:15:32.542 --> 00:15:34.542
The energetic, cheerful,

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:37.750
the one who puts
a smile on everyone's faces…

00:15:38.625 --> 00:15:39.917
For me, Derby is…

00:15:44.208 --> 00:15:45.292
Kita?

00:15:45.292 --> 00:15:46.333
Diamond.

00:15:46.333 --> 00:15:48.458
I think I can do it.

00:15:48.458 --> 00:15:50.667
I'll go and get some taiyaki.

00:15:50.667 --> 00:15:53.042
Yes, I'll be fine.

00:15:53.583 --> 00:15:57.667
Derby is just a festival.

00:15:57.667 --> 00:15:59.500
And I love festivals.

00:15:59.500 --> 00:16:01.500
So, I…

00:16:02.042 --> 00:16:03.500
"SPECIAL TAIYAKI"
Two taiyakis, please.

00:16:03.500 --> 00:16:04.625
"SPECIAL TAIYAKI"
Custard and…

00:16:04.625 --> 00:16:05.917
"SPECIAL TAIYAKI"
Custard for both.

00:16:08.458 --> 00:16:11.667
The Japanese Derby will begin soon.

00:16:11.667 --> 00:16:15.792
How will the horse girls perform?
What will happen?

00:16:15.792 --> 00:16:18.750
We are all waiting for the answers.

00:16:18.750 --> 00:16:19.792
Mr. Yamamoto.

00:16:19.792 --> 00:16:21.542
Pleased to work with you today.

00:16:21.542 --> 00:16:23.375
Likewise.

00:16:24.125 --> 00:16:26.208
Winning this race

00:16:26.208 --> 00:16:29.583
means you are the fastest
and the No. 1 horse girl in the world.

00:16:29.583 --> 00:16:32.792
They will do their best
to bring us a thrilling race.

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:37.708
This is Derby.

00:16:37.708 --> 00:16:39.583
I will run happily, joyfully.

00:16:39.583 --> 00:16:40.917
I will be my true self.

00:16:41.417 --> 00:16:43.333
Remember, your pacing is very important.

00:16:43.333 --> 00:16:45.417
Don't be intimidated
by the atmosphere or your rivals.

00:16:45.417 --> 00:16:47.042
All the best.

00:16:47.042 --> 00:16:50.042
Kita, you have this.

00:16:50.042 --> 00:16:53.083
Enjoy the nervousness too.

00:16:53.792 --> 00:16:54.750
Kita.

00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:57.958
Be yourself, okay?

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.000
Yes!

00:17:01.500 --> 00:17:04.167
Here she is,
the highly-anticipated horse girl.

00:17:04.583 --> 00:17:05.708
"DURAMENTE, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
She won Satsuki Sho

00:17:05.708 --> 00:17:07.791
"DURAMENTE, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
with her overwhelming speed.

00:17:07.791 --> 00:17:09.207
"DURAMENTE, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
I hope she can get the triple crown.

00:17:09.875 --> 00:17:12.291
She showed us the burst
she is capable of in Nakayama.

00:17:12.291 --> 00:17:13.832
In this long, straight running track,

00:17:13.833 --> 00:17:15.917
will we witness her burst again?

00:17:16.500 --> 00:17:18.541
"SATONO CROWN, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
Next, Satono Crown.

00:17:18.541 --> 00:17:20.166
"SATONO CROWN, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
On her quest to winning G1,

00:17:20.166 --> 00:17:22.207
"SATONO CROWN, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
what will she show us today?

00:17:22.625 --> 00:17:25.208
Her previous score does not
put her in an advantageous position

00:17:25.208 --> 00:17:27.000
but if she finds her rhythm here,

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:29.625
she can and will win this race.

00:17:30.625 --> 00:17:33.167
I can't lose. I must win.

00:17:33.167 --> 00:17:34.458
I

00:17:34.458 --> 00:17:36.958
will break this curse.

00:17:36.958 --> 00:17:38.917
Here, the 3rd place in Satsuki Sho,

00:17:38.917 --> 00:17:40.458
Kitasan Black.

00:17:40.458 --> 00:17:44.167
I heard she trained very hard
for this race.

00:17:44.167 --> 00:17:46.458
She does not look fatigued though.

00:17:46.458 --> 00:17:48.375
She looks motivated.

00:17:48.375 --> 00:17:49.458
I can't wait for her performance.

00:18:01.333 --> 00:18:06.208
That was where I cheered for Teio.

00:18:09.708 --> 00:18:10.708
All right then.

00:18:12.250 --> 00:18:14.000
G1, JAPANESE DERBY, TOKYO YUSHUN
TOKYO RACECOURSE, 2,400M COURSE

00:18:33.083 --> 00:18:37.042
The biggest race that decides
the champion of horse girls,

00:18:37.042 --> 00:18:39.375
Tokyo Yushun, Japanese Derby.

00:18:39.375 --> 00:18:41.000
18 horse girls, each carrying a dream

00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:43.292
on their shoulders

00:18:43.292 --> 00:18:45.625
enter the starting gate.

00:18:46.625 --> 00:18:48.750
Everything is in position now.

00:18:48.750 --> 00:18:50.667
May destiny lead them to their glory.

00:18:50.667 --> 00:18:53.625
No, they will earn glory with sheer will!

00:18:53.625 --> 00:18:55.375
Start!

00:18:55.375 --> 00:18:57.792
6 had a later start,

00:18:57.792 --> 00:19:00.208
but everyone was off to a great start.

00:19:00.208 --> 00:19:02.958
Which one of them will reach
the spectator's stand first?

00:19:02.958 --> 00:19:04.375
-Go!
-Will it be

00:19:04.375 --> 00:19:05.292
America Spike?

00:19:05.292 --> 00:19:08.250
Kitasan Black approached the middle now.

00:19:08.250 --> 00:19:09.500
Ribbon Pia is in the lead,

00:19:09.500 --> 00:19:11.042
but how long can she maintain it?

00:19:11.042 --> 00:19:12.792
Kitasan Black is following closely behind.

00:19:12.792 --> 00:19:14.292
The cheering is loud.

00:19:14.292 --> 00:19:16.792
As if it could crush me.

00:19:16.792 --> 00:19:18.000
But…

00:19:21.583 --> 00:19:25.333
We're now heading to the most difficult
part, the first bend.

00:19:25.333 --> 00:19:27.708
The luckiest one
will always win the Derby.

00:19:27.708 --> 00:19:30.375
Such as Eishin Flash,
Tanino Gimlet, and Special Week.

00:19:30.375 --> 00:19:33.667
Records show it's usually won
by the third place of Satsuki Sho.

00:19:33.667 --> 00:19:34.750
Why is that?

00:19:34.750 --> 00:19:37.167
Do you know who is the third place
in this year's Satsuki Sho?

00:19:37.167 --> 00:19:39.083
That's right. It's Kitasan Black.

00:19:40.958 --> 00:19:42.333
I see.

00:19:42.333 --> 00:19:45.125
After the difficult second bend,
they have arrived at the straight.

00:19:45.125 --> 00:19:46.750
Let's see who has the lead.

00:19:46.750 --> 00:19:48.208
Ribbon Pia is first,

00:19:48.208 --> 00:19:49.750
followed by Kitasan Black.

00:19:49.750 --> 00:19:51.167
Duramente is in the middle.

00:19:51.167 --> 00:19:53.958
Can Satono Crown redeem herself here?

00:19:53.958 --> 00:19:57.917
It says 58.8 seconds
when they crossed the 1,000-meter mark.

00:19:57.917 --> 00:19:59.042
Too fast.

00:19:59.042 --> 00:20:01.250
Kita got carried away.

00:20:01.250 --> 00:20:06.167
The sun is glaring
in the Tokyo Racecourse.

00:20:06.167 --> 00:20:08.792
She's the only one ahead of me.

00:20:08.792 --> 00:20:11.625
I can see the finishing line now.

00:20:11.625 --> 00:20:13.417
We are now at the fourth bend.

00:20:13.417 --> 00:20:17.000
After this is the final stretch.

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:19.208
Everything is at stake.

00:20:19.208 --> 00:20:20.083
-I can do this.
-Everything is at stake.

00:20:20.083 --> 00:20:21.583
-From here to the finishing line…
-The final stretch of this race.

00:20:21.583 --> 00:20:22.333
-I have to win.
-The final stretch of this race.

00:20:22.333 --> 00:20:23.625
-I must win.
-Go.

00:20:23.625 --> 00:20:26.292
Kitasan Black and Ribbon
are going neck and neck.

00:20:26.292 --> 00:20:28.833
Go!

00:20:28.833 --> 00:20:30.958
Ribbon will not concede either.

00:20:30.958 --> 00:20:33.042
I'm so close. So close.

00:20:34.583 --> 00:20:36.875
They won't give up that easily.

00:20:36.875 --> 00:20:38.792
Kitasan Black is still chasing.

00:20:38.792 --> 00:20:41.458
Will one of them win this race?

00:20:41.458 --> 00:20:42.958
But it's too early to say.

00:20:42.958 --> 00:20:44.958
This long final stretch

00:20:44.958 --> 00:20:47.708
is their one-way ticket to glory.

00:20:47.708 --> 00:20:51.000
18 horse girls are giving their all.

00:20:52.333 --> 00:20:53.792
Here she is.

00:20:53.792 --> 00:20:56.000
Duramente accelerated.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:58.833
I won't lose. The fight is just starting!

00:20:58.833 --> 00:21:01.708
The final 200 meters!

00:21:08.458 --> 00:21:12.167
Duramente is in the lead.

00:21:12.917 --> 00:21:15.083
No. The finishing line is not here yet.

00:21:15.083 --> 00:21:19.208
Duramente takes the lead!

00:21:19.833 --> 00:21:22.042
Duramente!

00:21:22.833 --> 00:21:24.875
Duramente!

00:21:24.875 --> 00:21:26.583
She is so fast.

00:21:26.583 --> 00:21:29.542
She overtook everyone.

00:21:29.542 --> 00:21:33.792
Duramente got two crowns!

00:21:33.792 --> 00:21:36.667
No one can stop her!

00:21:36.667 --> 00:21:39.000
She overtook everyone in seconds!

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:40.167
Incredible!

00:21:40.167 --> 00:21:45.500
Duramente has obtained
two of the three crowns!

00:21:45.500 --> 00:21:48.125
Yes!

00:21:48.125 --> 00:21:49.375
What is her ranking?

00:21:49.375 --> 00:21:50.792
I think…

00:21:50.792 --> 00:21:52.042
14th.

00:21:52.042 --> 00:21:54.292
If I'm not mistaken.

00:21:54.292 --> 00:21:56.958
2 minutes 23.2 seconds.

00:21:56.958 --> 00:21:59.583
That is the record for this year's Derby.

00:21:59.583 --> 00:22:02.208
Without a doubt, it's a landslide victory!

00:22:02.208 --> 00:22:04.750
Please cheer for Duramente!

00:22:23.583 --> 00:22:26.250
I lost…

00:22:27.305 --> 00:23:27.768
